name: Hainan Airlines 787-9 Dreamliner [B-7880] Landing at Calgary Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Hainan Airlines typically serves Calgary with their Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner three times a week. This past Saturday was an exception however, when they sent one of their 787-9s for the first time since the route started almost a year ago now. Hopefully more equipment swaps like this happen in the future, and especially with one of Hainan's Kung Fu Panda 789s! ATC is included, hope you enjoy this special arrival video.

Thanks for watching!
